      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Clough for SC5</h3>
        <p class="text-ivory-300 mb-6 max-w-md">
          Conservative leadership for South Carolina District 5. Join us in
          making our community stronger, freer, and more prosperous.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
